==Mitauro==

Pakuverengwa kwemitauro yemuAfrica , kunozni ziwumbe iri rine mitauro inosvika zviuru zviviri, (2000). Mitauro iyi mizhinji ndeymueAfrica asi kune imwewo yakauya kubva kuEurope neAsia. Kunozni Africa ndiyo nzvimbo ine vanhu vanotaura mitauro mizhinji pane dzimwe dzose.
